# Benchmark run outputs (raw and aggregate alike) are regenerable and live only alongside a run.
# The study's data of record is the committed RESULTS.md / DX.md, not a tree of per-run files, so
# the whole results/ directory stays out of the repo (main carries the lean study, not the pile).
docs/benchmarks/**/results/
docs/benchmarks/**/.build/
# Node tooling (VS Code extension) and build artifacts.
**/node_modules/
*.vsix
